project.name: ActiveBPEL
project.description: ActiveBPEL Community Edition Engine is an open source implementation of a BPEL engine which reads BPEL process definitions and creates representations of BPEL processes. ActiveBPEL is written in Java and runs in any standard servlet container (for example, Apache Tomcat). The ActiveBPEL project also includes support for the BPEL Extensions for People and WS-Human Task.
